msgstr "应对代码进行性能分析以找出瓶颈，并采取相应措施。以下分析工具可能对您有所帮助："

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/performance-tuning.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "<!-- - [Yii debug toolbar and debugger](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-debug/blob/master/docs/guide/README.md) -->\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
